<a name="activity"></a>
<div class="callout newsfeed">{{{dashboard_news}}}<div class="newsimage" style="background-image:url({{dashboard_news_img}})"></div></div>

<br />

{{#platform_type_single}}
	{{^elements_found}}
	<div class="gettingstarted">
		<h4>You're done installing, now let's get started</h4>
		So the database is set up and if you're seeing this all the configuration is right. There are just 
		a few easy steps before you publishing your first working CASH Music element.

		<br /><br />

		<div class="col_oneofthree{{#step1_complete}} complete{{/step1_complete}}">
			<h4>Step 1: System stettings</h4>
			<p>
				Before you go too far you should change default settings like the system email and the time-zone. Add any 
				third-party connections you want to start using.
			</p>
			<a href="{{www_path}}/settings/" class="featured"><i class="icon icon-cog"></i>Email and time-zone</a><br />
			<a href="{{www_path}}/settings/connections/" class="featured"><i class="icon icon-cogs"></i>Connect services</a>
		</div>

		<div class="col_oneofthree{{#step2_complete}} complete{{/step2_complete}}">
			<h4>Step 2: Add your stuff</h4>
			<p>
				The platform works with your content and your world — so start by adding an MP3 or setting up an email list. 
			</p>
			<a href="{{www_path}}/assets/" class="usecolor1 featured"><i class="icon icon-file"></i>Add a new asset</a><br />
			<a href="{{www_path}}/people/" class="usecolor2 featured"><i class="icon icon-list-ul"></i>Create an email list</a>
		</div>

		<div class="col_oneofthree lastcol">
			<h4>Step 3: Publish!</h4>
			<p>
				You're ready to create your first element. Try something simple like an email capture element. Point
				to an existing list, maybe offer a download, and then embed with the code you're given.
			</p>
			<a href="{{www_path}}/elements/add/" class="usecolor5 featured"><i class="icon icon-plus-sign"></i> Add your first element</a>
		</div>

		<br /><br /><br />
		<span class="helpspc"><b>Need more help?</b> Check out the <a href="{{www_path}}/help/gettingstarted/" class="helplink">Getting Started</a> page.</span>
	</div>
	{{/elements_found}}
{{/platform_type_single}}

{{^current_page_template}}
	<div class="callout bright flush">
		<h4>Publish a page</h4>
		<p>You can publish a page with any of your elements. Bring your own markup and just drop in any CASH element embed code(s) you want. Look below for details.</p>
		{{^defined_page_templates}}
			<br />
			<a href="{{www_path}}/elements/templates/add/"><i class="icon icon-list-alt"></i><b>Add a page template to start</b></a>
		{{/defined_page_templates}}
	</div>
{{/current_page_template}}

<a name="elements"></a>
<br />
<h4>Elements</h4>
<div class="row">
	<div class="eight columns">
		{{#elements_for_user}}
		<ul class="alternating">
			{{#elements_for_user}}
			<li>
				<b>{{name}}</b> <span class="descriptive spaced fadedtext">{{type_name}}</span>
				<div class="itemnav">
					<a href="{{www_path}}/elements/edit/{{id}}" class="mininav_flush"><i class="icon icon-search"></i>Details</a> 
					<a href="{{www_path}}/elements/delete/{{id}}" class="mininav_flush needsconfirmation"><i class="icon icon-ban-circle"></i> Delete</a>
				</div>
			</li>
			{{/elements_for_user}}
		</ul>
		{{/elements_for_user}}

		{{^elements_for_user}}
		<p>No elements have been added yet.</p>
		{{/elements_for_user}}
	</div>
	<div class="four columns">
		<p>
			You can add as many elements as you like. They’re the building blocks of the CASH platform. <a href="{{www_path}}/help/gettingstarted/">Learn more.</a>
		</p><p>
			Start here.
		</p>
		<a href="{{www_path}}/elements/add/" class="button"><i class="icon icon-plus-sign"></i>Add a new element</a>
	</div>
</div>

<a name="publish"></a>
<br />
<h4>Publish / embed</h4>
	{{#current_page_template}}
	<div class="row">
		<div class="twelve columns">
			<p class="big tight">
				Your public page is live at <a href="{{user_page_uri}}" target="_blank"><i>{{user_page_display_uri}}</i></a>
			</p>
			<a href="{{www_path}}/account/" class="usecolor0"><i class="icon icon-user"></i><b>Change your username/url</b></a>
			<br /><br /><br />
		</div>
	</div>
	{{/current_page_template}}
	<div class="row">
		<div class="six columns spacedtext">
			<label>Your public page</label>
			
			<a href="{{www_path}}/elements/templates/add/"><i class="icon icon-list-alt"></i><b>Add a new page</b></a><br />
			<a href="{{www_path}}/elements/templates/edit/{{current_page_template}}"><i class="icon icon-pencil"></i><b>Edit the current page</b></a><br />

			<div class="drawer noprefix">
				<a class="drawerhandle fullsize"><i class="icon icon-columns"></i><b>Publish a different page</b></a>
				<div class="drawercontent">
					<br />
					<form method="post" action="">
						<label for="template_id">Select a page template to publish:</label>
						<select id="change_template_id" name="change_template_id">
							{{{template_options}}}
						</select>
						<br />
						<button type="submit"><i class="icon icon-desktop"></i>Publish</button>
					</form>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="six columns spacedtext">
			<label>Element embed codes / templates</label>
			
			<a href="{{www_path}}/elements/templates/add/"><i class="icon icon-list-alt"></i><b>Add a new embed template</b></a><br />
			
		</div>
	</div>
</div>